problem statement:

for corporate unit head who wants to manage the mailbox size due to the sheer number if emails that they
receive during long travel, this e-mobile solution provides a sync up of the mail box with their computer
email for sending and receiving messages. unlike other email solution, this solution is secure and ensures
real time connectivity via internet. we want to make this avilable in next two month to our existing 
corporate customer.

components            value
target market         existing corporate customers
what is the product?  e-mobile solution
unique selling points secure and real time connectivity via internet
differentiator        sync up of mail box in phone with computer email
target timeframe      2 months

    
